== Ibikorwa ==

[[Image:Kizito Mihigo received Cyrwa AWARD.JPG|thumb|Kizito Mihigo ahembwa na Jeannette Kagame, CYRWA award i [[Kigali]] - Kanama 2011]]
Guhera mu mwaka wa 2011, ku bufatanye na Ambassade ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hamwe n'umuryango World Vision International, Fondation KMP yatangiye ubukangurambaga mu mashuri yo mu Rwanda no muri za gereza zose zo mu gihugu. Muri Kanama 2011 Kizito Mihigo yahawe igihembo na Madamu Jeannette Kagame kubera ibikorwa by'iyi fondation biharanira amahoro n'ubwiyunge <ref>[http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2011-08-20/84730/ First Lady awards Young Rwandan Archivers]
 - The New Times (Mu Cyongereza), 21 Kanama 2011 </ref> 

Muri Werurwe 2013, KMP yahawe igihembo igihembo n'Ikigo cy'igihugu cy'imiyoborere (RGB)  nk'umwe mu miryango itari iya Leta ikora ibikorwa bifasha igihugu mu miyoborere myiza<ref>[http://greatlakesvoice.com/civil-society-organs-win-rgb-grants/ Civil Society Organs win RGB awards]
 - Great Lakes Voice (Mu Cyongereza), 21 Mata 2013 </ref>

Fondation KMP yahagaritse ibikorwa ibikorwa y a York muri Mata 2014 ubwo umuhanzi Kizito Mihigo yafungwaga na Leta azira ubyaha byo gushaka guhirika ubutegetsi bwa FPR Inkotanyi, na Perezida wa Repuburika Paul Kagame <ref name="arrestation">[http://rfi.fr/afrique/20140416-rwanda-kagame-karegeya-kizito-mihigo-fdlr-rnc-fpr-attaque-police/ Rwanda: quatre personnes arrêtées, dont le chanteur Kizito Mihigo]
 - [[RFI]] (Mu Gifaransa), 16 Mata 2014 </ref> 

